                                   About
                                   -----

 Some months ago i started to program in C on Amiga. Initially, i wrote some
 simple utilities and last week, when i was very boring to load DOpus to 
 view some fonts, i decided to write a command to do this. So, i ran my text
 editor and i started to write the first simple version of ShowFont.
 
 From the last week, ShowFont has been updated a lot of times. Now, this is 
 the final version. 

 This archive should include:
 
  * ShowFont                     - The program
  * ShowFont.guide               - Amigaguide Docs
  * ShowFont.doc                 - Docs

 ShowFont simply load a font opening an Intuition Window and displays some
 infos about it.

 ShowFont has been tested on:

 - A500 KS1.2 & A500 K1.3 1 MB RAM (512C+512F)
 - A1200 KS3.1 Std.

 For more infos about ShowFont use, sinply @{" Click Here " link SF_Use}.

@endnode

