@node SF_Use "ShowFont / Use"
@toc  main
@prev SF_Reqs
@next SF_Distribution

                                    Use
                                    ---

 Using ShowFont is very simple. Simply write:

 ShowFont [fontname.font] <size>

 Font name must end with ".font". Size is optional. If you don't specify
 a size, ShowFont will display the font with the lowest one.

 If anything goes right, ShowFont will open a window displaying a phrase 
 using the selected font. ShowFont also prints on a CLI window some infos
 about the font (name, size, lower char, higher char, baseline...).

 ShowFont also displays Color fonts in the opened window. At the moment, 
 Color font palette is not supported. ShowFont uses WB palette.

@endnode

