@node SF_Bugs "ShowFont / Bugs"
@toc  main
@prev SF_Distribution
@next SF_History

                                   Bugs
                                   ----

 At the moment ShowFont has a bug only. This one is caused probably by the
 compiler because source is really bug free. No gurus, however.

 When you quit from ShowFont clicking on the window close gadget, ShowFont
 doesn't free allocated memory. So, you have to use some commands such as
 Avail Flush or Flush to recover un-used memory.

 Sorry! I'll change the compiler. ;-)

@endnode

